  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of Delafloxacin versus Vancomycin plus
      Aztreonam in the treatment of patients with complicated bacterial and soft tissue
      infections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
